      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable and well-maintained vehicle! It's in good condition, showing clear evidence of consistent care and attention throughout its life. It drives smoothly and is ready to provide many more miles of reliable service for its next owner. This is a fantastic opportunity to own a solid car that has been treated right!",
