    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, essentially indistinguishable from a brand-new car. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep showroom shine, and the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. Every feature and electronic component works exactly as it did the day it left the factory; this is truly a collector-quality example for the most discerning buyer.",
