    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior remains clean with only minor surface blemishes consistent with regular use, and the interior is well-kept, showing slight wear on the driver's seat bolster but no tears or stains. Mechanically, it performs excellently, with all major systems functioning as intended and a consistent service history. Buyers can expect a dependable, attractive car that is ready for daily driving without needing immediate repairs.",
