      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade vehicle of unparalleled caliber. This specimen resides in pristine, showroom-quality condition, exhibiting an uncompromising level of preservation and mechanical excellence. Meticulously maintained to the highest standards, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior appointments, reflects its status as an exemplary model of its class.",
